  "image_directives": "clean dealership photography. Vehicles on lit lots at dusk, detail shots of grilles and wheels, salespeople walking customers through paperwork without staged smiles. Avoid balloon-and-banner lot-sale aesthetics. No flame graphics. Real customers shaking hands beside their new keys, soft natural light, slight wide-angle for inventory rows. Showroom interiors should look swept and organized, not glossy.",
